data.description: Don't miss out on this gorgeous & highly upgraded home that surpasses the charm of new construction. The home is open & spacious with an abundance of natural light. The expansive gourmet kitchen features stainless steel appliances and ample counter & cabinet space for all your culinary needs. The timeless upgrades throughout the home include....a remodeled half bath, upgraded light fixtures, durable vinyl flooring, 6" baseboards, upgraded carpeting, wood accent ceilings, water softener, raised garden bed and so much more! Upstairs you'll find all the bedrooms, two full baths, and a game room. The spacious primary suite has a walk-in closet & an oversized shower. The beautiful backyard retreat has a 400sqft covered patio and offers plenty of space to run & play. The highly sought-after Creekside community has a sparkling pool that is within walking distance from the house. The home is conveniently located close to I-35, The Shops at Creekside, restaurants, a drive-in theater, Freiheit Country Store, Lake Dunlap, Lake McQueeney, Canyon Lake, river activities, Bucees, and the San Marcos outlets. Award-winning Comal ISD schools. WELCOME HOME!
